 Bug Title: Phone number fields Allows for Invalid Phone Numbers

Description: The home and mobile phone number fields in Address accepts any numerical value

The steps reequired to reproduce: Register for an account, enter email address which takes you to the address page. Enter any invalid phone number in the phone number fields.

Environment: Google Chrome

Expected results: Error message stating the need for a valid number for the field.

Assigned to: Vedang Kolhatkar

Severity: Minor
